title: How to Clean Jet

steps.headline: Dip a soft rag into olive oil.
Rub gently over the jet to remove any particles and to bring it to a shine.
Polish up using a chamois cloth.
steps.description: This will remove any excess oil.

text: Dip a soft rag into olive oil.  Rub gently over the jet to remove any particles and to bring it to a shine.  Polish up using a chamois cloth. This will remove any excess oil.
